<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.4.5">
<l>vampu lāmkūn talmaṇṭō tarikā talaṉvāṉpuka</l>
<l>vampu taṉṉāl muṉinta vaḻaka ṉiṭameṉparāl</l>
<l>umpar kōṉu mulakē ḻumvantīṇ ṭivaṇaṅkunal</l>
<l>cempo ṉārum matiḷcūḻn taḻakār teṉṉaraṅkamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They truly say that the place of the comely one who raged with arrows</l>
<l>So that the beloved of Maṇḍodari, with hair that wafted fragrance,</l>
<l rend="indent">entered heaven,</l>
<l>Is Araṅkam of the South, filled with beauty, with walls covered</l>
<l rend="indent">with fine, rose gold encircling [it],</l>
<l> Where, coming together, the celestials’ king and the seven worlds worship.</l> 
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
